{
  "id": "adv_main_03_01_03",
  "title": "BIG4編1章3話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_backstage-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――数日後",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "――それで、スリクスのみなさんは\n星見プロに入ることになったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the members of ⅢX\nHave joined Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。とはいえ、しばらくの間はお試し期間だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But it's a trial period for now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 13.3404762586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うちと合わないと思ったら\nスリクスは即時契約を打ち切ってもいいことになってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they feel it doesn't work out\nⅢX can terminate the contract immediately",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、あくまでとりあえずって感じなんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so it's more of a tentative arrangement",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6355332375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 23.4355332375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それに、三人とも今みんながいる寮には入らない\nマンションで引き続き一人暮らしをするそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ none of the three will move into the dorm where everyone else is\nThey'll continue living alone in their apartments",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "向こうも、俺達となれ合うつもりはないらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems they don't intend to get too close to us either",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3975288709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.8615650337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、ちょっと残念です\nいっぱいお話ししてみたいなって思ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's a bit disappointing\nI was hoping to talk with them a lot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……スリクスの事務所入りに反対しないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're not against ⅢX joining our agency?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 43.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　だって、あんなに凄い人達なんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But they're such amazing people‚ aren't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "どんな風に練習してるのかとか\nお休みは何をしてるのかとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to know how they practice\nWhat they do on their days off…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 53.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "聞きたいことが沢山あるなって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's so much I want to ask!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか、さくららしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see‚ that's just like you‚ Sakura",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 60.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、麻奈さんの歌を奪おうとした理由は\nずっと気になってましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Also‚ I've always been curious about\nThe reason they tried to take Mana-san's songs",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 67.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、一度ちゃんとお話を聞いてみたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I'd like to hear their side of the story properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな。いずれは聞いてみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right. We should listen to them someday",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……そんな話、聞けるのかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-But… can we really hear such a story…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 74.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 80.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん？　どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa? Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 82.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "だって……話を聞いてると\nなんだかとっても怖いイメージだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… from what I've heard\nThey sound kind of scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 89.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "普段は猫さん、かぶってる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do they wear… cat masks normally…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……まあ、素の性格は個性的かもしれないな\n……少しだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ their true personalities might be quite unique\n…Just a bit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 99.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "少しって……どこがですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A bit… where exactly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 102.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ。素を見せた時だけ怖いって話でしょ？\nそれなら普段は怖くないってことじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now. They're only scary when they show their true selves‚ right?\nThat means they're not scary usually",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……これからはオフモードのスリクスに\n会うタイミングは沢山……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… from now on‚ we'll have many chances…\nTo meet ⅢX in off-mode…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 119.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ。あはは……そっかー、同じ事務所だもんね\n顔を合わせることはいくらでもあるか～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah. Ahaha… That's right‚ we're in the same agency now\nWe'll be seeing them a lot~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 129.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、フォローどころか……逆効果……ブルブル",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ that's not helping… it's making it worse… shiver",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 134.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
